data.description: This beautiful solid brick ranch style home is a true gem nestled on a picturesque 1.86-acre lot, offering all the space you need for relaxation and outdoor activities. Inside, you'll find a cozy abode featuring 3 bedrooms and 1 bath, with stunning hardwood floors flowing throughout, exuding warmth and charm. The kitchen boasts modern granite countertops, perfect for culinary enthusiasts. Convenience is key with a 1st-floor laundry setup, making daily chores a breeze. And that's not all - the full basement provides an excellent opportunity for expansion, more storage, or creating recreational space. No more parking woes as the property offers a paved driveway and a carport. Additional storage is available in the shed, making organization easy. Affordable utilities and taxes too!  If you are looking to simplify, down-size, or make a fresh new start, this is the perfect place!
